UOVRNuKHGXpE5b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711201111294xrNl2DkjfPt7muZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711201111299MgudQOJ4KUCl5EG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711201111297zLbpT2qNfha8UVs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111130fQYJXZzUy1h5c7Ca.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111130vbFQdkymP05RAMY6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111130o6cwLe83tv1FnbgW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111131tpRrx3ZDH9nM6AF4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.452020\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>做水桶包出名的 <a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2017/11/mansur-gavriel-wallets\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mansur Gavriel</a> 发布了首个钱包系列，包括售价 195 美元的卡包，以及 395 美元的钱包，延续了一贯的简约设计和丰富的色彩。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711201111588Bf2a3DwIS0ZK9pY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111159u8OtRhU4dMgGyESV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111200c4FYubvL2Ca1RZMd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.508296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111200mUQjJ8KghA1Padkr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.508296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711201112006I3hKyXPWneZozpN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>11 月 18 日下午 4 点至 11 点，<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/vetements-hong-kong-pop/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vetements </a>在香港启德邮轮码头开设了一个仅有 7 个小时的快闪店。现场布置的像是个 DHL 的周边市场，有 DHL 提供的厢式货车、Vetements 和 Umbro 的联名款等，居然还卖起了心形维他命磁石、印着风景画的马克杯这样的旅游市场必备小商品。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111326H6S9ADPk4dr3ZgsF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111328gv1uzrnp7b3yRXxM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111330nf3I4SzdNXc8M1G0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111330ltJVnEBc7bgaS2OL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111330bn0B2XN9UZ4C1ha3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111331Ni2gDbskj1cKB48e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111331MgQjUR6qNfxSePsb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111333txw3Mm0hebuEonJT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711201113343lANZspkgxhrw42a.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111335RM4JgjH1qLwoldvy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171120111335VhndcSYT7X1ki9Cy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 